<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>

    <!-- importacion de bootstrap -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Libre+Franklin:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap');

        html {
            font-family: "Libre Franklin", sans-serif;
            font-optical-sizing: auto;

        }

        .img-principal {
            height: 200px;
            width: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        nav {
            background: #9dc7ff;
        }

        nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #000;
        }

        section h3 {
            margin-top: 12px;
        }

        section a {
            color: #000;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            height: 80px;
            padding: 12px;
        }
    </style>

    <nav class="nav d-flex justify-content-around w-100 p-3">
        <div><a href="">Servicios</a></div>
        <div><a href="">Conocenos</a></div>
        <div><a href="">Información de contacto</a></div>
    </nav>

    <main class="container position-relative text-center mt-3">
        <h1>ServiceDEV</h1>
        <p>Conoce los servicios que ofrecemos para la venta de recursos tecnológicos en la provincia de Ubaté</p>
        <article class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row container-fluid ">
            <section class="card justify-content-center align-items-center col d-flex m-2 ">
                <h3>Servicios</h3>
                <img class="img-principal" src="img/servicios.jpeg" alt="imagen de">
                <a href="">Servicios de venta de productos electrónicos.</a>
            </section>
            <section class="card justify-content-center align-items-center col d-flex m-2 flex-column">
                <h3>Conocenos</h3>
                <img class="img-principal" src="img/contactos.jpeg" alt="imagen de">
                <a href="">Conoce la historia de nuestra empresa.</a>
            </section>
            <section class="card justify-content-center align-items-center col d-flex m-2 flex-column">
                <h3>Contactanos</h3>
                <img class="img-principal" src="img/contactos.jpeg" alt="imagen de">
                <a href="">Conoce más información de contacto.</a>
            </section>
        </article>

    </main>


    <h4>
        <%= message%>
    </h4>

    <!-- importacuion de script en bootstrap.js
      -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.8/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-I7E8VVD/ismYTF4hNIPjVp/Zjvgyol6VFvRkX/vR+Vc4jQkC+hVqc2pM8ODewa9r"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-0pUGZvbkm6XF6gxjEnlmuGrJXVbNuzT9qBBavbLwCsOGabYfZo0T0to5eqruptLy"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>